snippet.title: Lala Lala (Official Video) | Simiran kaur Dhadli | New Punjabi Song 2025
snippet.description:
Simiran Kaur Dhadli is back with a brand new banger LALA LALA – the Party Anthem of 2025!

Title : LaLa LaLa 
Singer/Lyrics/Composer : Simiran Kaur Dhadli 
Mix master -Mixboy
Music : Desi Trap 
Video : Honey Virk 
Project Managed By : Sahejpal Singh Sidhu 
Special Thanx : Ishtmeet Singh Phull , Ripple & Garry
Dop - jpal pannu
Production - Ten plus one production uk
Casting - Francesca uk
Make up & Mua - Munmeet kaur uk
Editor / DI colorist - Honey Virk Films
Promotions by - Bull18 Network
Choreographer - Rijul kaushal 
Pre - production india - Bawa maan
_______________________________________________________

Lyrics :

loki puchhde ne kudi kitho ayi aa,
lala lala pyi jatti ne karayi a,
kali gaddi ohdi firey vairi ghoor di,
te hoodie paune 3 lakh vali payi a,
oh lala lala pyi jatti ne krai aaa…

Dabkaundi munde akkh mutiyaar dii,
jdo seesheeyan cho bahar nigah maar di,
rakkhe khabbi seat thalle hiqq cheerna,
puthi matt bol mada ni sahaar di..
kudi vehle baith rabb ne bnai a,
kalle kalle gunn utte dise reej lai aa,
tahii lala lala Lala…….
tahi lala lala lala
oh lala lala pai jatti ne krayi aa….


kehlo hankaar chahe kehlo gall maan diii,
samje na kise nu v apne oh haan di,
                           x2
jandi aa pachhani add dooron hi rakaan,
rohab kahda akkh vich maut da smaan,
Paya gall vich baaz mare barrkaaaa,
jatti da ruger 
fire kadd da sariaaa rarkaa..
jatti da ruger 
fire kadd da sariaaa rarkaa..x2

aye hye kina sohna lagge rohab odi akkh ch,
challe hawa to khilaaf aasmaan ohde pakh ch,
                                x2
vadde vadde khabbikhana nu oh khangan ni dindi,
din antiaa da saukha koi langan ni dindi,
kudi jidde de game vich ai aa,
paisa ni kamaya balle balle hi kmayii aa,
ohh tahi lala lala ……….
                    x2
oh lala lala payiii jatti ne krayi aaaaa…..

snippet.title: People We Meet On Vacation | Official Teaser | Netflix
snippet.description:
Every summer for nearly a decade, free-spirited Poppy and buttoned-up Alex embark on a travel adventure, but after years of not speaking, one fateful trip brings them back together to confront their unspoken feelings for one another.

Based on the global best selling book by Emily Henry, People We Meet On Vacation comes to Netflix January 9, starring Emily Bader & Tom Blyth.

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81764371

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with over 300 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

People We Meet On Vacation | Official Teaser | Netflix
https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix

Lyrics:

Lost in emotion, mama's youngest
Tryna navigate life without my compass
Some experience death and feel numbness
But not me, I felt it all and couldn't function
Seein' you that day
Tellin' you my plans but I was leavin' you that day
It was in God's hands, Ye was at Elon's waiting to get with me
On my way to Texas, that's when Virginia hit me
And I realized in that instant
Our last conversation, you was against it
Told you I was going to Turks for Thanksgiving
I heard what I wanted to hear but didn't listen
You said you told Gene that Bup needed forgiveness
I see you went to DD's and stuffed both her fridges
You even told Dad you wished y'all never splitted
See, you were checkin' boxes, I was checkin' my mentions
Sayin' you was tired but not ready to go
Basically was dying without lettin' me know
I loved you met Nige, hate that he won't remember you
Two things that break my heart is what Novembers do
And T follows you, now mind you
DD calls you, Gene finds you, was that your vision?
Precision, while I'm reminiscin'
It all hits different
Ma, listen

The birds don't sing (yeah)
The birds don't sing, they screech in pain, pain
The birds don't sing (oh)
The birds don't sing, they screech in pain (oh, they screech in pain)
The birds don't sing
The birds don't sing, they screech in pain

Your car was in the driveway, I knew you were home
By the third knock, a chill ran through my bones
The way you missed Mama, I guess I should've known
Chivalry ain't dead, you ain't let her go alone
Found you in the kitchen, scriptures in the den
Half-written texts that you never got to send
Combin' through your dresser drawer, where do I begin?
Postin' noted Bible quotes, were you preparin' then?

snippet.title: The Mandalorian Isn't Going To Save Star Wars
snippet.description: The first trailer for The Mandalorian And Grogu movie came out a few days ago, and nobody cared. Which is a bit of a problem when its the first theatrical Star Wars release in six years, and desperately needs to succeed if its to resurrect the franchise. Can Jon Favreau's movie hope to succeed? Will Pedro Pascal have ANOTHER flop to add to his resume? Does anyone even care?
